OL,3,CThe inspiring schoolchildren on a
OL,4,Cmission to make sure no child goes
OL,5,Chungry
OL,7,FSchool dinner time is always busy, but
OL,8,Fit can also be costly. The children at
OL,9,FMonksdown Primary School in Liverpool
OL,10,Fenjoy hot lunches, but many are paying
OL,11,Faround 2 pounds a day, so more than
OL,12,Ften pounds a week.
OL,14,FIt is a cost that mounts up for
OL,15,Ffamilies already feeling the pinch in
OL,16,Fthe cost of living crisis.
