OL,5,Chungry
OL,7,FSo the children have gone right to the
OL,8,Ftop, writing to the Prime Minister and
OL,9,Fjoining a national campaign urging the
OL,10,FGovernment to provide free school
OL,11,Fmeals to every child in England.
OL,13,FOne pupil said "I think it's terrible
OL,14,Fbecause Scotland, Wales and London
OL,15,Fhave free school meals so why can't
OL,16,FEngland."
OL,18,FAnother said "When you are in year 2
OL,19,Fyou don't have to pay, but when you
OL,20,Fare in year 3 parents have to put
OL,21,Faside like lots and lots of money"
