OL,7,FThere is a foodbank known as the
OL,8,Fpantry and it is right on the school
OL,9,Fplayground. It is packed full of
OL,10,Fessential items and this all provides
OL,11,Fa lifeline to many families at the
OL,12,Fschool who come there every Tuesday
OL,13,Fwhen it is open. The school say they
OL,14,Fhave seen an increase in demand
OL,15,Fshowing more and more families need a
OL,16,Fhelping hand.
