OL,5,Chungry
OL,7,FTeacher Marie Ferrigan siad "It's
OL,8,Factually the family where two wages
OL,9,Fare coming in where on paper they have
OL,10,Fa steady wage and they don't actually
OL,11,Fqualify for anything at all. That's
OL,12,Fwhy the free school meal came about
OL,13,Fwhen we were looking at it. It was
OL,14,Fthose families who were using the
OL,15,Fpantry."
OL,17,FIt's a year since free school meals
OL,18,Fwere extended to every child in London
OL,19,Fand already the benefits are clear
OL,20,Fwith nearly 80% of parents saying it
OL,21,Fhas helped their budget.
