OL,7,FIn a statement the department for
OL,8,Feducation said:
OL,10,F"We want to give every child the best
OL,11,Fstart in life and we understand the
OL,12,Fpressures many households are under,
OL,13,Fwhich is why we have doubled the
OL,14,Fnumber of children receiving free
OL,15,Fschool meals since 2010 from one sixth
OL,16,Fto one third"
